# Enforce LF line endings across all text files so the byte-identity
# regression test (tests/scripts/byte-identity-regression.test.mjs) is
# platform-stable. Without this, Windows checkouts (with core.autocrlf=true)
# produce CRLF working trees while Linux CI runners produce LF, and the
# adapter bundle emit hashes diverge per-platform.
#
# `* text=auto eol=lf` lets git auto-detect text vs binary; binaries are
# left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
